â€œSo overall, Iâ€™d choose HashMap for single-threaded or read-heavy scenarios where thread-safety isn't a concern. But for concurrent applications like caching, I'd go with ConcurrentHashMap due to its fine-grained locking and better performance under multi-threaded access.â€